This study is designed to assess the safety and feasibility of using the ExAblate, Type 2 to temporarily disrupt the blood brain barrier in non-enhancing suspected glioblastomas.

 The ExAblate Model 4000 Type-2 is intended for use as a tool to disrupt the BBB.

